moon or Downing Suites, otherwise it is 7.50 per person.'),(2587,206,'_module_builder_rooms_3_article_0_content','field_5dc1a1f1b568a'),(2588,206,'module_builder_rooms_3_article_0_color','Pink'),(2589,206,'_module_builder_rooms_3_article_0_color','field_5dc1a1f1b56cb'),(2590,206,'module_builder_rooms_3_article','1'),(2591,206,'_module_builder_rooms_3_article','field_5dc1a1f1b09fe'),(2592,206,'module_builder_rooms_2_room_1_heading','Hotel Suites'),(2593,206,'_module_builder_rooms_2_room_1_heading','field_5dc1b7b8250f0'),(2594,206,'module_builder_rooms_2_room_1_content','The Downing and Honeymoon Suites are perfect for luxury stays. Recently refurbished, these spacious suites are beautifully furnished with soft fabrics and restful hues.\r\n\r\n<strong>Both suites have:</strong>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Well-stocked hospitality tray</li>\r\n<li>Digital TV with freeview</li>\r\n<li>Telephone</li>\r\n<li>Ensuite bathroom</li>\r\n<li>Hairdryer</li>\r\n<li>Irom</li>\r\n<li>Soft bedding</li>\r\n<li>Luxury toiletries</li>\r\n</ul>'),(2595,206,'_module_builder_rooms_2_room_1_content','field_5dc1b7bf250f1'),(2596,206,'module_builder_rooms_2_room_1_gallery','a:1:{i:0;s:3:\"204\";}'),(2597,206,'_module_builder_rooms_2_room_1_gallery','field_5dc1b7ac250ef'),(2598,10,'module_builder_rooms_2_contents','                <p>The Downing Suite has been dedicated in memory of Mr Bernard Downing, a much-loved member of our hotel team. It has a spacious bathroom with an impressive walk-in shower. The Honeymoon Suite offers beautiful views over Brampton Gardens. It has a glamorous bathroom with the pice de rsistance  a double-ended bath</p>\r\n                <p>Room service is available during restaurant serving hours. Laundry services are available during the week and a safety deposit service is also provided.</p>\r\n                <p>Free parking and WiFi is available throughout your stay.</p>'),(2599,10,'_module_builder_rooms_2_contents','field_5dc1bf5b90d13'),(2600,208,'module_builder_rooms