nts_0_hero_slider','field_5dc28f7956493'),(2660,243,'module_builder_events','a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"slider\";}'),(2661,243,'_module_builder_events','field_5dc28f7954192'),(2662,20,'module_builder_events_1_heading','When you have a special event to mark, theres only one way to celebrate, and thats in style.'),(2663,20,'_module_builder_events_1_heading','field_5dc28f7979d91'),(2664,20,'module_builder_events_1_content','With two private event suites, a charming lounge bar, a recently refurbished restaurant (seating 60), and 40 bedrooms, our welcoming hotel resonates with the sound of laughter and celebration throughout the year. Our long-standing team can help you plan original and memorable celebrations and important events, taking care of all the details, so you can sit back, relax and cherish time spent with your guests.\r\n\r\nWe can host intimate occasions for just a handful of special friends, as well as push-the-boat-out, grand parties, celebrations and weddings for up to 120 people...plus everything in-between!\r\n\r\nFrom baby showers to birthdays, weddings to golden anniversaries, conferences to retirement celebrations, we are experienced and conscientious. We will provide everything you need - impeccable service and the kind of professional expertise that thinks of everything - leaving you to relax in the knowledge that you are in safe hands. We promise to be very clear in our pricing and approach, so youll know exactly what to expect.\r\n\r\nPlease call 01782 629421 or email info@borough-arms-hotel.co.uk to discuss your event'),(2665,20,'_module_builder_events_1_content','field_5dc28f797b2fe'),(2666,20,'module_builder_events_1_button_text',''),(2667,20,'_module_builder_events_1_button_text','field_5dc28f797c640'),(2668,20,'module_builder_events_1_button_url',''),(2669,20,'_module_builder_events_1_button_url','field_5dc28f797db9c'),(2670,244,'module_builder_events_0_hero_slider_0_image','242'),(2671,244,'_module_builder_events_0_hero_slider_0_image','field_5dc28f797