ing_0_hero_slider','1'),(2697,246,'_module_builder_dining_0_hero_slider','field_5dc063a6421b7'),(2698,246,'module_builder_dining_1_heading',''),(2699,246,'_module_builder_dining_1_heading','field_5dc063a6470ac'),(2700,246,'module_builder_dining_1_content','With a relaxed ambiance, attentive service, and menus full of British fare and the best of continental tastes, its clear that food is important to us here at the Borough Arms Hotel. You can choose to dine in Bar26, or the recently refurbished [RESTAURANT NAME],  both are popular with hotel guests and locals alike.\r\n\r\nWe aim to produce fantastic food without compromise. Whatever the occasion, our chefs create beautifully presented dishes, cooked to perfection using the best ingredients, with more than just a hint of flair! Dietary requirements and preferences are happily catered for, as are private dining parties and events. As our regulars will tell you, we pride ourselves on devilishly tasty food at a fair price.\r\n<hr />\r\n<h3>Food is served:</h3>\r\n<p>Monday to Saturday</p>\r\n\r\n<p>12:00  14:00 &amp; 18:00  21:00</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sunday Lunch</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>12:00  14:00</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sunday lunch is available from just 8.95 per person, take a look at our menu...</p>\r\n\r\n<p>For guests staying with us, a hearty breakfast is served from 7:00 - 9:00 Monday  Friday, or 8:00 - 10:00 Saturdays, Sundays and Bank Holidays</p>\r\n\r\n'),(2701,246,'_module_builder_dining_1_content','field_5dc063a6480a3'),(2702,246,'module_builder_dining_1_button_text',''),(2703,246,'_module_builder_dining_1_button_text','field_5dc063a6492dc'),(2704,246,'module_builder_dining_1_button_url',''),(2705,246,'_module_builder_dining_1_button_url','field_5dc063a64a722'),(2706,246,'module_builder_dining_2_image_and_text_grid_0_image','143'),(2707,246,'_module_builder_dining_2_image_and_text_grid_0_image','field_5dc16362e15b1'),(2708,246,'module_builder_dining_2_image_and_text_grid_0_heading','Restaurant'),(2709,246,'_modul