he-boat-out, grand parties, celebrations and weddings for up to 120 people...plus everything in-between!\r\n\r\nFrom baby showers to birthdays, weddings to golden anniversaries, conferences to retirement celebrations, we are experienced and conscientious. We will provide everything you need - impeccable service and the kind of professional expertise that thinks of everything - leaving you to relax in the knowledge that you are in safe hands. We promise to be very clear in our pricing and approach, so youll know exactly what to expect.\r\n\r\nPlease call 01782 629421 or email info@borough-arms-hotel.co.uk to discuss your event'),(2777,251,'_module_builder_events_1_content','field_5dc28f797b2fe'),(2778,251,'module_builder_events_1_button_text',''),(2779,251,'_module_builder_events_1_button_text','field_5dc28f797c640'),(2780,251,'module_builder_events_1_button_url',''),(2781,251,'_module_builder_events_1_button_url','field_5dc28f797db9c'),(2782,251,'module_builder_events_2_image_and_text_grid_0_image','247'),(2783,251,'_module_builder_events_2_image_and_text_grid_0_image','field_5dc28f79a536c'),(2784,251,'module_builder_events_2_image_and_text_grid_0_heading','Weddings'),(2785,251,'_module_builder_events_2_image_and_text_grid_0_heading','field_5dc28f79a53dc'),(2786,251,'module_builder_events_2_image_and_text_grid_0_content','Magnis ipsum arionse nduntetus ent voloreicimet labo. Nam iuriand ionsendit et quia volupta eptatint ut accus as aut audame natemol uptate culparc iditibus.'),(2787,251,'_module_builder_events_2_image_and_text_grid_0_content','field_5dc28f79a5416'),(2788,251,'module_builder_events_2_image_and_text_grid_1_image','248'),(2789,251,'_module_builder_events_2_image_and_text_grid_1_image','field_5dc28f79a536c'),(2790,251,'module_builder_events_2_image_and_text_grid_1_heading','Function& Parties'),(2791,251,'_module_builder_events_2_image_and_text_grid_1_heading','field_5dc28f79a53dc'),(2792,251,'module_builder_events_2_image_and_text_grid_1_content','Magn